    *   Thumbnails of pre-configured terrains (Canyon, Mountain, Coastal).
    *   One-click load functionality.
*   Export features:
    *   Download heightmap as PNG/EXR.
    *   Export simulation parameters as JSON.
    *   Share link generation (URL-encoded parameters).

